<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Members</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to external CSS file -->
    <style>
        /* Internal CSS styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #003366;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        section {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .member {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .member:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }
        .member-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        .member-role {
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>About Our Members</h1>
</header>

<section>
    <div class="member">
        <h2 class="member-name">John Doe</h2>
        <p class="member-role">Founder & CEO</p>
        <p>John Doe is the founder and CEO of our organization. He is responsible for leading the team and guiding our vision.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="member">
        <h2 class="member-name">Jane Smith</h2>
        <p class="member-role">Marketing Director</p>
        <p>Jane Smith oversees our marketing efforts and develops strategies to promote our brand and products.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="member">
        <h2 class="member-name">Michael Johnson</h2>
        <p class="member-role">Lead Developer</p>
        <p>Michael Johnson is our lead developer, responsible for managing our software development projects and ensuring quality code.</p>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
